# Web patterns

- Use App Router; server components for data fetch, client components for forms
- API routes return `NextResponse.json()` with correct status codes
- Validate request bodies with Zod schemas from `@the-syndicate/shared`
- Use `requireSession()` from `@/lib/api-auth` on protected routes
- Tailwind only; dark theme tokens in `globals.css`
- Prefer `prisma` from `@the-syndicate/database` — never raw SQL
